<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-36-0390 </DOCNO><TEXT>Recent progress concerning the production and applications of positroniumbeams is described. Both tunable, narrow energy width beams and sourcesof thermal positronium are included. A discussion of the motivation forexperimentation with positronium is given. 38 refs.; 9 figs.; 1 table.Contains author index</TEXT></DOC>